cc69dc82-a9ac-4773-a67b-73883d3cb100	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	The Importance of Marketing for a Business	business-sentence-importance-of-marketing	H├úy viß║┐t mß╗Öt ─æoß║ín v─ân ngß║»n (khoß║úng 80-150 tß╗½) vß╗ü tß║ºm quan trß╗ìng cß╗ºa marketing ─æß╗æi vß╗¢i mß╗Öt doanh nghiß╗çp. Bß║ín c├│ thß╗â n├│i vß╗ü c├ích marketing gi├║p sß║ún phß║⌐m ─æ╞░ß╗úc biß║┐t ─æß║┐n, thu h├║t kh├ích h├áng, hoß║╖c tß║ío dß╗▒ng th╞░╞íng hiß╗çu.	Discuss how marketing helps businesses sell products or services.	80	150	B1	SENTENCE	1	t	2026-07-14 19:00:18.495	2026-07-14 19:00:18.495	20	\N	0	Marketing is very important for any business. It helps companies show their products or services to many people. For example, good marketing can make customers know about a new phone or a tasty restaurant. It also helps businesses understand what customers want and need. When a business markets well, it can attract more customers and make more sales. Marketing builds the brand name, too. People will remember the company and trust it. Without marketing, even the best product might not find its buyers. So, marketing is key to a business's success and growth in today's world.
78f7954d-ae89-4a21-abf5-3827e5c47c60	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	What Makes Good Customer Service?	business-sentence-good-customer-service	H├úy viß║┐t mß╗Öt ─æoß║ín v─ân ngß║»n (khoß║úng 80-150 tß╗½) ─æß╗â m├┤ tß║ú nhß╗»ng yß║┐u tß╗æ tß║ío n├¬n dß╗ïch vß╗Ñ kh├ích h├áng tß╗æt. Bß║ín c├│ thß╗â ─æß╗ü cß║¡p ─æß║┐n sß╗▒ th├ón thiß╗çn, giß║úi quyß║┐t vß║Ñn ─æß╗ü nhanh ch├│ng, hoß║╖c lß║»ng nghe kh├ích h├áng.	Explain the qualities of excellent customer service.	80	150	B1	SENTENCE	2	t	2026-07-14 19:00:18.516	2026-07-14 19:00:18.516	20	\N	0	Good customer service is vital for any business. First, being friendly and polite to customers is very important. Customers like to feel welcome and respected. Second, businesses should listen carefully to what customers say, especially when they have a problem or a question. It shows that the company cares. Third, solving customer issues quickly and efficiently is key. Nobody likes to wait a long time for a solution. Good customer service also means understanding the product well so you can give correct information. When customers have a good experience, they are more likely to come back and recommend the business to others. This helps the business grow and build a good reputation.
94c9c647-72e5-4c8d-a368-3943f01e2cfa	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	Teamwork in the Workplace	business-sentence-benefits-of-teamwork	H├úy viß║┐t mß╗Öt ─æoß║ín v─ân ngß║»n (khoß║úng 80-150 tß╗½) vß╗ü nhß╗»ng lß╗úi ├¡ch cß╗ºa l├ám viß╗çc nh├│m trong m├┤i tr╞░ß╗¥ng c├┤ng sß╗ƒ. Bß║ín c├│ thß╗â n├│i vß╗ü viß╗çc chia sß║╗ ├╜ t╞░ß╗ƒng, giß║úi quyß║┐t vß║Ñn ─æß╗ü hiß╗çu quß║ú h╞ín, hoß║╖c tß║ío kh├┤ng kh├¡ l├ám viß╗çc t├¡ch cß╗▒c.	Explain why working as a team is good for a company.	80	150	B1	SENTENCE	3	t	2026-07-14 19:00:18.522	2026-07-14 19:00:18.522	20	\N	0	Teamwork is very beneficial in any workplace. When people work together, they can share different ideas and perspectives. This often leads to more creative solutions for problems. For example, one person might have an idea, and another can improve it. Working as a team also helps to complete tasks faster because responsibilities can be divided. Everyone can focus on their part. Moreover, teamwork creates a more positive and supportive work environment. Employees feel connected and motivated when they help each other. It also helps new employees learn faster from their experienced colleagues. Overall, teamwork improves productivity and makes the company more successful.
1b34c7ee-d255-402d-94f2-9dbc2e9a640c	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	Starting a Small Business: Common Challenges	business-sentence-challenges-small-business	H├úy viß║┐t mß╗Öt ─æoß║ín v─ân ngß║»n (khoß║úng 80-150 tß╗½) vß╗ü nhß╗»ng th├ích thß╗⌐c phß╗ò biß║┐n m├á mß╗Öt doanh nghiß╗çp nhß╗Å mß╗¢i th├ánh lß║¡p c├│ thß╗â gß║╖p phß║úi. Bß║ín c├│ thß╗â n├│i vß╗ü vß║Ñn ─æß╗ü t├ái ch├¡nh, cß║ính tranh, hoß║╖c t├¼m kiß║┐m kh├ích h├áng.	Discuss some difficulties faced by new small businesses.	80	150	B1	SENTENCE	4	t	2026-07-14 19:00:18.53	2026-07-14 19:00:18.53	20	\N	0	Starting a small business can be very exciting, but it also comes with many challenges. One major problem is often funding. New businesses might not have enough money to buy equipment, pay salaries, or market their products. Another big challenge is competition. There are often many established businesses selling similar products or services, so new businesses need to find a way to stand out. Finding and keeping customers is also difficult at first. People don't know the new brand, so building trust takes time and effort. Also, small business owners need to learn many different skills, from accounting to sales. Overcoming these challenges requires hard work, good planning, and a strong will to succeed.
ed5820d1-d5bd-49dc-a73f-42638709dfdc	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	How Technology Helps Businesses Grow	business-sentence-technology-in-business	H├úy viß║┐t mß╗Öt ─æoß║ín v─ân ngß║»n (khoß║úng 80-150 tß╗½) vß╗ü c├ích c├┤ng nghß╗ç gi├║p c├íc doanh nghiß╗çp ph├ít triß╗ân. Bß║ín c├│ thß╗â n├│i vß╗ü viß╗çc giao tiß║┐p dß╗à h╞ín, l├ám viß╗çc hiß╗çu quß║ú h╞ín, hoß║╖c tiß║┐p cß║¡n thß╗ï tr╞░ß╗¥ng rß╗Öng lß╗¢n h╞ín.	Explain the role of technology in modern business operations and growth.	80	150	B1	SENTENCE	5	t	2026-07-14 19:00:18.539	2026-07-14 19:00:18.539	20	\N	0	Technology plays a huge role in helping businesses grow today. Firstly, it makes communication much easier and faster. Companies can use email, video calls, and instant messaging to talk with employees and customers all over the world. This saves time and money. Secondly, technology helps businesses work more efficiently. Software can automate many tasks, like managing customer data or tracking sales, which reduces errors and frees up employees for more important work. Thirdly, the internet and social media allow businesses to reach a much larger market than before. They can sell products online to customers everywhere. Also, technology helps companies analyze data to understand customer behavior better. All these aspects help businesses become more competitive and successful.
