bfa3a252-311d-4412-bcf0-deee4f4947b8	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	The Value of Teamwork in Business	business_opinion-value-teamwork-business	Trong mß╗Öt c├┤ng ty, l├ám viß╗çc nh├│m c├│ quan trß╗ìng kh├┤ng? H├úy giß║úi th├¡ch l├╜ do tß║íi sao l├ám viß╗çc nh├│m lß║íi cß║ºn thiß║┐t (hoß║╖c kh├┤ng cß║ºn thiß║┐t) cho sß╗▒ th├ánh c├┤ng cß╗ºa mß╗Öt doanh nghiß╗çp. Bß║ín ─æ├ú bao giß╗¥ l├ám viß╗çc trong mß╗Öt nh├│m ch╞░a? Chia sß║╗ kinh nghiß╗çm cß╗ºa bß║ín.	Discuss the importance of teamwork in a company setting.	80	150	B1	OPINION	2	t	2026-07-14 19:01:31.808	2026-07-14 19:01:31.808	20	\N	0	Yes, teamwork is very important in a company. When people work together, they can share different ideas and solve problems more quickly. Each person has different skills, so they can help each other. For example, one person might be good at writing, and another good at design. Together, they can create a better project. Teamwork also makes the workplace happier and more positive because people feel supported. I once worked in a team for a school project, and we finished it faster and got a better result because we divided the tasks and helped each other. It was a good experience.
ae431b4f-6882-4385-99bf-50d9201a4e80	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	Profit or People: Which Comes First?	business_opinion-profit-vs-people	Mß╗Öt sß╗æ ng╞░ß╗¥i tin rß║▒ng mß╗Ñc ti├¬u ch├¡nh cß╗ºa c├íc c├┤ng ty l├á kiß║┐m lß╗úi nhuß║¡n. Nhß╗»ng ng╞░ß╗¥i kh├íc lß║íi cho rß║▒ng c├íc c├┤ng ty n├¬n ─æß║╖t sß╗⌐c khß╗Åe v├á hß║ính ph├║c cß╗ºa nh├ón vi├¬n l├¬n h├áng ─æß║ºu. Bß║ín ─æß╗ông ├╜ vß╗¢i quan ─æiß╗âm n├áo h╞ín? H├úy giß║úi th├¡ch l├╜ do cß╗ºa bß║ín v├á ─æ╞░a ra v├¡ dß╗Ñ.	Share your opinion on whether companies should prioritize profit or employee well-being.	80	150	B1	OPINION	3	t	2026-07-14 19:01:31.815	2026-07-14 19:01:31.815	20	\N	0	I believe that companies should prioritize the well-being of their employees. When employees are happy and healthy, they work much better. They are more motivated, more productive, and more loyal to the company. If a company only focuses on profit, employees might feel stressed or undervalued, which can lead to low morale and high staff turnover. This can actually hurt profits in the long run. For example, companies that offer good benefits like flexible working hours or health programs often have happier staff and, as a result, achieve greater success. Happy employees are the foundation of a successful business.
9737e1c1-9afc-4360-9b6b-8677c5bd2d94	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	The Power of Marketing	business_opinion-power-marketing	Marketing (tiß║┐p thß╗ï) ─æ├│ng vai tr├▓ nh╞░ thß║┐ n├áo trong sß╗▒ th├ánh c├┤ng cß╗ºa mß╗Öt doanh nghiß╗çp? Theo bß║ín, mß╗Öt chiß║┐n l╞░ß╗úc marketing tß╗æt cß║ºn c├│ nhß╗»ng yß║┐u tß╗æ g├¼? H├úy ngh─⌐ vß╗ü mß╗Öt sß║ún phß║⌐m hoß║╖c dß╗ïch vß╗Ñ m├á bß║ín biß║┐t c├│ chiß║┐n dß╗ïch marketing th├ánh c├┤ng.	Discuss the role and importance of marketing for a business.	80	150	B1	OPINION	4	t	2026-07-14 19:01:31.821	2026-07-14 19:01:31.821	20	\N	0	Marketing plays a very important role in the success of any business. It helps people know about a company's products or services. Without good marketing, even the best product might not sell well because no one knows about it. A good marketing strategy needs to be creative and clear. It should show why the product is special and how it can help customers. It also needs to reach the right people. For example, Coca-Cola is famous for its marketing campaigns. Their advertisements are often emotional and memorable, which makes people feel good about the brand and want to buy their drinks. Good marketing builds brand loyalty.
9405f00b-5844-44ef-9775-93914d0e71af	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	Entrepreneurship vs. Employment	business_opinion-entrepreneurship-vs-employment	Nhiß╗üu ng╞░ß╗¥i trß║╗ m╞í ╞░ß╗¢c bß║»t ─æß║ºu c├┤ng viß╗çc kinh doanh cß╗ºa ri├¬ng m├¼nh, trong khi nhß╗»ng ng╞░ß╗¥i kh├íc th├¡ch l├ám viß╗çc cho mß╗Öt c├┤ng ty ─æ├ú c├│ sß║╡n. Theo bß║ín, lß╗▒a chß╗ìn n├áo tß╗æt h╞ín? H├úy tr├¼nh b├áy ╞░u v├á nh╞░ß╗úc ─æiß╗âm cß╗ºa tß╗½ng lß╗▒a chß╗ìn v├á ─æ╞░a ra quan ─æiß╗âm c├í nh├ón.	Compare starting your own business with working for an existing company.	80	150	B1	OPINION	5	t	2026-07-14 19:01:31.826	2026-07-14 19:01:31.826	20	\N	0	Both starting your own business and working for a company have their pros and cons. Starting your own business gives you a lot of freedom. You can be your own boss, choose your hours, and follow your passions. There's also potential to earn a lot of money if it's successful. However, it's very risky and takes a lot of hard work and responsibility. You might not have a stable income at first. Working for a company, on the other hand, offers more stability and a regular salary. You have fewer worries about big business decisions and can learn from experienced colleagues. Personally, I think working for a company first is a good idea to gain experience and learn skills before thinking about starting your own business later.
ca48e096-7c82-43a0-9847-fa829c08d102	3409773a-8b22-4d4e-80af-a8bec2940f66	The First Customer	business-story-the-first-customer	Bß║ín l├á chß╗º mß╗Öt qu├ín c├á ph├¬ mß╗¢i mß╗ƒ. Mß╗ìi thß╗⌐ ─æ├ú sß║╡n s├áng cho ng├áy khai tr╞░╞íng. Nh╞░ng ngay khi kh├ích h├áng ─æß║ºu ti├¬n b╞░ß╗¢c v├áo, mß╗Öt vß║Ñn ─æß╗ü bß║Ñt ngß╗¥ ─æ├ú xß║úy ra. H├úy kß╗â lß║íi c├óu chuyß╗çn vß╗ü ng├áy ─æß║ºu ti├¬n ─æ├│ v├á c├ích bß║ín giß║úi quyß║┐t t├¼nh huß╗æng.	Imagine you've just opened your dream caf├⌐. Everything is ready, but then an unexpected problem arises on your very first day.	80	150	B1	STORY	1	t	2026-07-14 19:01:49.892	2026-07-14 19:01:49.892	20	\N	0	My heart was beating fast. Today was the grand opening of 'Coffee Dream,' my new caf├⌐. I had spent months preparing everything. The coffee machine was shiny, the pastries smelled wonderful, and the tables were set. At 9 AM, the first customer, an old lady with a kind smile, walked in. I was so excited! But then, a terrible noise came from the kitchen. The refrigerator stopped working! All my fresh milk and ingredients were at risk. I quickly apologized to the customer and called my friend, a mechanic. He arrived very fast and fixed it in 30 minutes. The old lady patiently waited and then ordered a latte. It was a stressful start, but I learned to stay calm under pressure.
